@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1) Categories with product count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/categories/stats?non_empty_only=true

### 2) New arrivals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?sort=createdAt:desc&limit=12

### 2b) New arrivals (public common endpoint for client home)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/common/products?sort=createdAt:desc&limit=12

### 2c) Search products (public common endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/common/products?q=%C3%A1o&sort=createdAt:desc&limit=6&page=1

### 3) Category showcases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category-showcases?categoryLimit=4&productLimit=3

### 4) Category showcases alias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/home/category-showcases?categoryLimit=4&productLimit=3

### 5) Cart summary (auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
